Title: Shooting Stars
Plot: The CSIs come across an abandoned military compound being used by a small cult. The CSIs grow suspicious when they see that a mass suicide has taken place, but only 11 of the 12 beds are occupied.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence,sexual themes and content that may disturb
